{"vv15:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv15:0.2":"Itthivimana ","vv15:0.3":"Pithavagga ","vv15:0.4":"15. Uttaravimanavatthu ","vv15:1.1":"“Abhikkantena vannena, ","vv15:1.2":"ya tvam titthasi devate; ","vv15:1.3":"Obhasenti disa sabba, ","vv15:1.4":"osadhi viya taraka. ","vv15:2.1":"Kena tetadiso vanno, ","vv15:2.2":"kena te idha mijjhati; ","vv15:2.3":"Uppajjanti ca te bhoga, ","vv15:2.4":"ye keci manaso piya. ","vv15:3.1":"Pucchami tam devi mahanubhave, ","vv15:3.2":"Manussabhuta kimakasi punnam; ","vv15:3.3":"Kenasi evam jalitanubhava, ","vv15:3.4":"Vanno ca te sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv15:4.1":"Sa devata attamana, ","vv15:4.2":"moggallanena pucchita; ","vv15:4.3":"Panham puttha viyakasi, ","vv15:4.4":"yassa kammassidam phalam. ","vv15:5.1":"“Issa ca maccheramatho palaso, ","vv15:5.2":"Nahosi mayham gharamavasantiya; ","vv15:5.3":"Akkodhana bhattu vasanuvattini, ","vv15:5.4":"Uposathe niccahamappamatta. ","vv15:6.1":"Catuddasim pancadasim, ","vv15:6.2":"ya ca pakkhassa atthami; ","vv15:6.3":"Patihariyapakkhanca, ","vv15:6.4":"atthangasusamagatam. ","vv15:7.1":"Uposatham upavasissam, ","vv15:7.2":"sada silesu samvuta; ","vv15:7.3":"Sannama samvibhaga ca, ","vv15:7.4":"vimanam avasamaham. ","vv15:8.1":"Panatipata virata, ","vv15:8.2":"musavada ca sannata; ","vv15:8.3":"Theyya ca aticara ca, ","vv15:8.4":"majjapana ca araka. ","vv15:9.1":"Pancasikkhapade rata, ","vv15:9.2":"ariyasaccana kovida; ","vv15:9.3":"Upasika cakkhumato, ","vv15:9.4":"gotamassa yasassino. ","vv15:10.1":"Saham sakena silena, ","vv15:10.2":"yasasa ca yasassini; ","vv15:10.3":"Anubhomi sakam punnam, ","vv15:10.4":"sukhita camhinamaya. ","vv15:11.1":"Tena metadiso vanno, ","vv15:11.2":"tena me idha mijjhati; ","vv15:11.3":"Uppajjanti ca me bhoga, ","vv15:11.4":"ye keci manaso piya. ","vv15:12.1":"Akkhami te bhikkhu mahanubhava, ","vv15:12.2":"Manussabhuta yamaham akasim; ","vv15:12.3":"Tenamhi evam jalitanubhava, ","vv15:12.4":"Vanno ca me sabbadisa pabhasatiti. ","vv15:13.1":"Mama ca, bhante, vacanena bhagavato pade sirasa vandeyyasi—","vv15:13.2":"‘uttara nama, bhante, upasika bhagavato pade sirasa vandati’ti. ","vv15:13.3":"Anacchariyam kho panetam, bhante, yam mam bhagava annatarasmim samannaphale byakareyya, tam bhagava sakadagamiphale byakasi”ti. ","vv15:14.1":"Uttaravimanam pannarasamam. "}